How to change the color for VIFM

    Go to vifmrc which is located in /.config/vifm/ folder
    Go inside colors/ and create a file with .vifm extension
    From the website below choose the best theme for you and paste it to the file

[[https://vifm.info/colorschemes.shtml|Scheme link to get different colors]]

* `t` to select multiple files 

